    "heroImage": "/images/reports/archive/details/report-from-ika-taikai-czech-republic/01.jpg",
    "excerpt": "The first IKA International Taikai took place in Karlovy Vary, Czech Republic in June this year. Instructors and students from Spain, Switzerland, Japan and the UK joined the Czech Federation for two days of competition and training. Congratulations to everyon",
    "contentHtml": "<div>\n\t\t\t\t<div>The first IKA International Taikai took place in Karlovy Vary, Czech Republic in June this year. Instructors and students from Spain, Switzerland, Japan and the UK joined the Czech Federation for two days of competition and training.</div>  <div><div> <a> <img src=\"/images/reports/archive/details/report-from-ika-taikai-czech-republic/01.jpg\" alt=\"Picture\" /> </a> <div></div> </div></div>  <div>Congratulations to everyone who took part in the tournament. First place results are below:<br /><br /><br />Dan Grade Kumi Embu &ndash; Daniel &amp; Domenico, City, BSKF<br />Kyu Grade Kumi Embu &ndash;&nbsp;<br />Dantai Embu &ndash; Mayfair branch, BSKF<br />Kyu Grade Tanen Embu &ndash; Michael, Karlovy Vary, CFSK<br />Dan Grade Tanen Embu &ndash; Ben, SOAS, BSKF<br />Shakujo Embu &ndash; Will, Mayfair, BSKF<br />Randori &ndash; Karl, SOAS, BSKF</div>\n\n\t\t</div>"
